<p>
  The
  {{code '<perk-grid>'}}
  element displays a grid of sponsorship packages and their perks using data from the Tilde Events App API.
</p>
<h3 {{anchor}}>
  Attributes
</h3>
<p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      {{code 'data-event-id'}} <i>(required)</i>: The ID corresponding to the event.
    </li>
    <li>
      {{code 'data-grid-title'}}: An optional title to be displayed in the first cell.
    </li>
    <li>
      {{code 'data-placeholder-text'}}: Optional placeholder text to override the default text displayed while the data is loading.
    </li>
    <li>
      {{code 'data-error-text'}}: Optional error text to override the default text displayed if there is an error while rendering the element.
    </li>
  </ul>
</p>